subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Restricted to headwater tributaries from the rio Paraíba do Sul and rio Doce basins, eastern Brazil ( Fig. 43 ). A old record for the lower rio Doce basin in Espírito Santo state (
MCZ 21104
) is here considered doubtful in view of the known preference of the species for headwater areas. See the item “Remarks”, below, for an account on the locality “ Bahia ” (type-locality of the holotype of
Brycon bahiensis
).
